  "title": "Intensely Crunchy Portuguese Fernbrake-Gosari Tagine",
  "description": "A pungent and crunchy Portuguese dish featuring fernbrake-gosari and lamination-puff, perfect for a crowd-pleaser. This whole30-friendly recipe is a twist on traditional tagines.",
  "cuisine": "portuguese",
