      "amount": "1/2 teaspoon"
    },
    {
      "name": "fresh parsley",
      "amount": "1/4 cup"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F.",
    "Chop onion and garlic.",
    "In a large pan, heat olive oil over medium heat. Add onion and garlic and cook until softened.",
    "Add gosari fernbrake and cook until tender.",
    "Add lamination-puff pastry and crumble into the pan.",
    "Pour in chicken broth and red wine vinegar.",
    "Sprinkle smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Transfer to a tagine pot and bake for 25 minutes.",
    "Garnish with fresh parsley and serve hot."
  ],
